  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the early metabolic responses (whole body and within muscle tissue) to a single
      day of whole body physical inactivity (i.e. bed-rest), and evaluate the contribution of
      inactivity per se vs alterations in diet
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
